S \sin(\theta) = \sum_{k=1}^n \dfrac{\left(\sin((2k+1) \theta) - \sin((2k-1) \theta) \right)}2
2S \sin(\theta) = \sin((2n+1) \theta) - \sin(\theta) = 2 \sin(n \theta) \cos((n+1) \theta)
